<i>she will not be able to study this year.</i>

00:14:57.240 --> 00:15:00.720
Okay, Mom, I’ll transfer the money.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:03.200
<i>Thank you, son.</i>

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.360
<i>I wont ask for anymore.</i>

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:07.720
<i>I’m so sorry.</i>

00:15:07.960 --> 00:15:11.560
<i>As soon as your dad returns,</i>
<i>I'll pay you back.</i>

00:15:12.760 --> 00:15:16.600
It’s alright, Mom.
I still have some savings.

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:18.960
I'll transfer it to you.

00:15:19.040 --> 00:15:23.560
If there isn’t anything else,
I’d better get back to work. Bye, Mom.

