Is that you, Ceen?

00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:43.160
<i>All your problems can be resolved</i>
<i>with one easy fix.</i>

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:44.680
<i>Money, right?</i>

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:47.760
If you don’t tell me
