00:48:31.120 --> 00:48:33.400
<i>and not leave them in solitude.</i>

00:48:33.480 --> 00:48:36.520
<i>This is the condition of the house</i>
<i>before Chew started neglecting it…</i>

00:48:36.600 --> 00:48:37.720
What the hell?

00:48:43.600 --> 00:48:47.160
-<i>You saw the TV, didn’t you?</i>
-Yes.

00:48:47.240 --> 00:48:50.080
<i>I’m going to give you an opportunity</i>
<i>to do a good deed for a change.</i>

00:48:50.160 --> 00:48:51.600
<i>A chance to help someone.</i>

00:48:51.640 --> 00:48:53.280
<i>That person is Chew.</i>

00:48:53.360 --> 00:48:55.360
<i>He's still inside this house.</i>

00:48:56.200 --> 00:48:57.240
What do I have to do?

00:48:57.280 --> 00:49:00.680
<i>Do you remember the well?</i>

00:49:00.920 --> 00:49:02.080
Yes.

00:49:03.280 --> 00:49:05.400
I’m looking for it right now.

00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:06.560
<i>Excellent.</i>

00:49:11.720 --> 00:49:13.360
<i>Chew is in the well.</i>

00:49:13.440 --> 00:49:17.600
<i>You have ten minutes to help him out.</i>

00:49:18.560 --> 00:49:20.480
How long has Chew been in there?

00:49:20.560 --> 00:49:22.200
<i>A little over ten days.</i>

00:49:22.280 --> 00:49:23.640
Ten days?

00:49:23.720 --> 00:49:25.600
And you knew he’d fallen in ten days ago?

00:49:25.640 --> 00:49:26.600
Why didn’t you help him?

00:49:26.680 --> 00:49:28.080
<i>It’s not our business.</i>

00:49:28.160 --> 00:49:31.200
<i>It’s the responsibility of his relatives</i>
<i>to care for him, isn’t it?</i>

00:49:31.240 --> 00:49:32.440
I guess.

00:49:33.200 --> 00:49:37.400
-But--
-<i>If you hurry he might still be alive.</i>

00:49:37.480 --> 00:49:41.240
<i>You have ten minutes starting</i>
<i>from when you hang up the phone.</i>

00:49:41.320 --> 00:49:43.520
<i>Help Chew from the well</i>

00:49:43.560 --> 00:49:46.360
<i>and get the telephone number</i>
<i>from his shirt pocket.</i>

00:49:46.440 --> 00:49:48.560
<i>Then call his relatives</i>
<i>to come pick him up.</i>

00:49:48.640 --> 00:49:52.960
<i>If you succeed, a cash prize</i>
<i>of 1.2 million Baht will be yours.</i>

00:49:53.040 --> 00:49:54.400
<i>Do you understand?</i>

00:49:54.440 --> 00:49:55.600
Okay.

00:49:56.320 --> 00:49:58.600
<i>If you understand, then start.</i>

00:53:34.240 --> 00:53:35.560
Uncle!

00:53:36.320 --> 00:53:38.680
Stop creeping me out.

00:53:38.720 --> 00:53:40.760
I’m trying to help you.

00:53:41.000 --> 00:53:44.160
Then your relatives
can have a proper funeral for you,

00:53:44.200 --> 00:53:46.560
and then you can rest in peace.

00:54:49.680 --> 00:54:53.520
Hello. Who do you wish to speak to?

00:54:53.560 --> 00:54:55.000
Hello, are you a relative of Chew’s?

00:54:55.080 --> 00:54:58.200
Nope. I'm just his nephew.

00:54:59.600 --> 00:55:00.520
Chew's fallen down the well. He's dead.

00:55:00.600 --> 00:55:02.760
<i>Come and pick up his body.</i>

00:55:04.240 --> 00:55:05.600
What was that?

00:55:05.640 --> 00:55:09.120
Chew's fallen down the well. He's dead.

00:55:09.200 --> 00:55:12.360
Who’s going to a water fall?

00:55:13.680 --> 00:55:15.320
Who was that?

00:55:22.000 --> 00:55:23.240
Muay, answer it!

00:55:23.320 --> 00:55:25.960
I can’t, I doing my nails? You get it!

00:55:26.040 --> 00:55:27.200
I'm playing a game. Can't you see?

00:55:27.280 --> 00:55:28.800
Well, can't you see what I'm doing?

00:55:29.000 --> 00:55:32.200
Aren't you a little too young
to be doing that?

00:55:32.680 --> 00:55:34.320
Hurry up and get the phone, will you?

00:55:34.400 --> 00:55:36.160
-You hurry up!
-Forget it!

00:55:36.240 --> 00:55:38.200
What's wrong with you two?
Can't you hear the phone?

00:55:38.240 --> 00:55:39.760
-Well, it's her--
-God, it's annoying.

00:55:40.000 --> 00:55:41.040
He won't pick it up.

00:55:41.080 --> 00:55:44.080
-Stop arguing, will you?
-Look, my fighter just died.

00:55:44.120 --> 00:55:45.160
I don't you what your problems are.

00:55:45.240 --> 00:55:48.080
What is so hard
about answering the damn phone?

00:55:48.120 --> 00:55:50.520
You’re useless, both of you!

00:55:52.360 --> 00:55:55.040
Hello, you’ve reached
the Chotisetianpaisarn residence.

00:55:55.120 --> 00:55:56.120
Are you a relative of Chew's?

00:55:56.160 --> 00:55:58.280
Not really, I'm just his son.

00:56:00.960 --> 00:56:03.640
Your father fell down the well.

00:56:04.680 --> 00:56:07.160
What did you say? I can’t hear you.

00:56:07.240 --> 00:56:09.760
Your dad drowned in the well.
Please come and get his body.

00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:12.400
Who? What? Who died?

00:56:12.440 --> 00:56:17.160
Your god damn father
drowned in the freaking well!

00:56:17.240 --> 00:56:18.640
No, your father died, asshole!

00:56:30.400 --> 00:56:35.560
Dad… the well… Dead!

00:56:39.600 --> 00:56:40.680
Dad!

00:56:42.200 --> 00:56:43.400
Oh, my God!

00:56:45.760 --> 00:56:49.360
Dad!

00:56:51.480 --> 00:56:53.200
Mommy!

00:56:53.280 --> 00:56:54.120
Dad!

00:56:54.200 --> 00:56:55.520
Mom!

00:56:55.600 --> 00:56:57.080
How the hell did you get in here?

00:56:58.360 --> 00:57:01.680
I heard about it on TV, so I stopped by.

00:57:02.960 --> 00:57:05.320
Are you a burglar?

00:57:07.440 --> 00:57:09.400
How dare you say that?

00:57:09.440 --> 00:57:11.440
I’m here to help.

00:57:11.520 --> 00:57:13.520
What kind of a family are you?
Didn't give a damn about your dad.

00:57:13.600 --> 00:57:14.480
You left him to drown.

00:57:14.560 --> 00:57:16.120
You've got some nerve!

00:57:16.680 --> 00:57:18.240
The coroner’s almost here

00:57:18.280 --> 00:57:20.680
and the police are on their way.

00:57:22.720 --> 00:57:25.120
Hey, where the hell
do you think you’re going?

00:57:25.200 --> 00:57:28.520
Stay and talk to the cops first,
Mr. Nice Guy.

00:57:30.680 --> 00:57:32.560
Mr. Nice Guy?

00:57:41.080 --> 00:57:43.000
Do you have any cigarettes?

00:58:00.040 --> 00:58:03.040
Tong, you’re working over time?

00:58:03.120 --> 00:58:05.240
Don’t work so hard.

00:59:27.960 --> 00:59:31.080
Maew. Maew. Maew.

00:59:31.160 --> 00:59:32.040
What!?

00:59:34.000 --> 00:59:36.360
Oh, Chit.

00:59:38.760 --> 00:59:40.760
Why are you walking away?

00:59:42.520 --> 00:59:45.520
I’m sorry. I didn’t know it was you.

00:59:47.520 --> 00:59:49.080
How are you?

00:59:53.960 --> 00:59:57.680
I’m sorry, but I need to get going.

01:00:00.360 --> 01:00:04.440
Maew, my mom says she misses you.

01:00:05.120 --> 01:00:08.520
She wants both of us
to visit her during the holidays.

01:00:11.040 --> 01:00:13.360
Phuchit, we’ve been through this.
We're finished.

01:00:13.440 --> 01:00:15.520
We can start over.

01:00:15.600 --> 01:00:16.640
Maew. I’ve changed.

01:00:16.720 --> 01:00:20.600
I can buy a house now.
I can even buy you a car.

01:00:20.680 --> 01:00:24.560
I can give you everything
you've ever wanted.

01:00:26.600 --> 01:00:28.720
Chit, stop it.

01:00:30.080 --> 01:00:32.240
I’ve heard this all before.

01:00:32.760 --> 01:00:35.440
I’ve wasted enough time on you.

01:00:36.840 --> 01:00:39.280
You should go home if you're drunk.

01:00:40.240 --> 01:00:42.680
I'm not drunk. I'm telling the truth.

01:00:42.720 --> 01:00:46.280
If you don’t believe me,
then take a look at my bank balance.

01:00:48.520 --> 01:00:49.720
Chit,

01:00:52.120 --> 01:00:53.800
even if you had

01:00:54.040 --> 01:00:56.480
all the money in the world,

01:00:56.560 --> 01:01:02.000
you still couldn't make me famous.

01:01:06.240 --> 01:01:07.600
Maew.

01:01:15.640 --> 01:01:18.080
Maew, I’ve been looking
everywhere for you. I'm so sorry.

01:01:18.120 --> 01:01:20.520
Leave me alone. That hurts.

01:01:21.560 --> 01:01:24.480
This is Phuchit, an acquaintance.

01:01:25.400 --> 01:01:27.360
Phuhit, this is Chalerm, my boyfriend.

01:01:29.160 --> 01:01:31.360
Maew, I’m sorry.
I won’t do this to you again.

01:01:31.440 --> 01:01:32.320
Chalerm!

01:01:32.360 --> 01:01:33.320
Come on?

01:01:33.360 --> 01:01:34.440
That hurts.

01:01:34.520 --> 01:01:36.600
I'm sorry. Please come back to me.

01:01:36.680 --> 01:01:39.480
-You always say that.
-I'll do anything.

01:01:52.480 --> 01:01:53.320
Hello.

01:01:53.400 --> 01:01:56.120
<i>100 million Baht is within your reach.</i>

01:01:56.160 --> 01:01:58.560
<i>Now it's time</i>
<i>to engage your brain a little.</i>

01:01:58.640 --> 01:02:00.720
<i>You’ll need a partner</i>
<i>for the next challenge.</i>

01:02:00.760 --> 01:02:03.960
<i>Do you remember</i>
<i>the number of this challenge?</i>

01:02:04.040 --> 01:02:05.560
-Of course.
-<i>Good.</i>

01:02:05.640 --> 01:02:08.080
<i>Then just look for something in the area</i>

01:02:08.160 --> 01:02:11.160
<i>that has the number eight</i>
<i>associated with it.</i>

01:02:17.640 --> 01:02:19.080
Then what?

01:02:19.160 --> 01:02:23.760
<i>Once you have found that number eight</i>
<i>on that particular person,</i>

01:02:24.000 --> 01:02:28.360
<i>you must take the object with number eight</i>
<i>and knock them out with it.</i>

01:02:28.440 --> 01:02:30.120
Why didn’t you just tell me that
in the first place?

01:02:30.200 --> 01:02:32.320
I'll be more then glad
to whack him with this chair.

01:02:32.400 --> 01:02:34.200
Why didn't you just say that?

01:02:34.280 --> 01:02:37.520
<i>Well, that’s how the script was written.</i>

01:02:40.360 --> 01:02:41.640
Chalerm!

01:02:46.200 --> 01:02:49.320
Stop! Phuchit, what are you doing?

01:02:49.400 --> 01:02:50.440
Maew…

01:02:53.840 --> 01:02:55.240
Chalerm! Chalerm!

01:03:02.080 --> 01:03:03.520
That's it.

01:03:03.600 --> 01:03:05.480
Maew, let me expla--

01:03:20.240 --> 01:03:21.520
Take this! Here!

01:03:24.040 --> 01:03:28.080
Why the hell
do you keep getting up? I’m tired.

01:03:34.360 --> 01:03:37.120
-Maew, let me explain.
-Chalerm! Chalerm!

01:03:37.200 --> 01:03:38.640
Chalerm!

01:03:46.560 --> 01:03:50.760
Honey, don't die.

01:03:51.520 --> 01:03:53.800
Please, get up.

01:03:55.040 --> 01:03:57.600
Chalerm…

01:03:58.240 --> 01:04:03.080
Please! Somebody please help us!

01:04:03.560 --> 01:04:06.480
Chalerm, please don’t die, okay?

01:04:10.320 --> 01:04:13.040
What are you going to do to him?

01:04:18.560 --> 01:04:21.200
Chalerm… Chalerm…

01:04:30.440 --> 01:04:32.360
VACANT

01:04:35.120 --> 01:04:37.280
Please take this man to the hospital.

01:04:37.360 --> 01:04:39.520
I don't think so. He’ll stain my seats.

01:04:39.600 --> 01:04:41.680
Forget it.
He'll get blood all over my car.

01:04:41.720 --> 01:04:43.480
Get the hell out, then!

01:04:43.520 --> 01:04:44.680
Maew, get him in the car.

01:04:46.800 --> 01:04:49.360
-Come out.
-What are you doing? Hey!

01:04:51.480 --> 01:04:53.360
Why are you punching me?

01:04:55.280 --> 01:04:57.240
Why did you punch me? Ouch!

01:05:04.240 --> 01:05:06.400
Help! This asshole is hi-jacking my car.

01:05:06.440 --> 01:05:10.080
Anybody! Help! He's taking my car.

01:05:18.120 --> 01:05:21.360
The office is closing.

01:05:36.240 --> 01:05:37.280
<i>It's an orange taxi.</i>

01:05:37.360 --> 01:05:38.560
<i>And what about the assailant?</i>

01:05:38.640 --> 01:05:40.360
<i>He's a guy dressed like an office worker.</i>

01:05:40.440 --> 01:05:42.800
<i>His clothes are filthy</i>
<i>and he's wearing glasses.</i>

01:05:43.040 --> 01:05:46.560
<i>Okay, we are coordinating activities</i>
<i>with Pol. Col. Surachai Tantiwiirakul,</i>

01:05:46.640 --> 01:05:48.680
<i>who is overseeing this case.</i>

01:05:48.720 --> 01:05:51.320
<i>It's believed that this case</i>

01:05:51.400 --> 01:05:53.200
<i>is related to an incident</i>
<i>that happened at 11am this morning.</i>

01:05:53.280 --> 01:05:56.160
Chalerm, you’ll be okay.

01:05:56.640 --> 01:06:00.400
You asshole, why did you do that?

01:06:00.480 --> 01:06:03.280
What if he dies? What will you do then?

01:06:03.360 --> 01:06:04.680
Maew, show me some respect.

01:06:04.760 --> 01:06:06.080
Why? Do you think
you’re some kind of saint?

01:06:06.160 --> 01:06:07.960
Look what he did to you!

01:06:08.040 --> 01:06:11.320
Am I supposed to ignore that he beats you?

01:06:11.400 --> 01:06:15.680
I'm may be an asshole,
but did I ever beat you like he did?

01:06:25.480 --> 01:06:27.120
Please help him.

01:06:28.560 --> 01:06:29.560
Help him, please.

01:06:31.360 --> 01:06:32.520
Chalerm, Chalerm.

01:06:39.120 --> 01:06:41.080
We're here, Chalerm.

01:06:55.800 --> 01:06:58.040
<i>At this time we have new developments</i>

01:06:58.120 --> 01:07:01.200
<i>in a case which is hitting the headlines.</i>

01:07:01.280 --> 01:07:05.120
<i>Police are currently on the look-out</i>
<i>for Mr. Phuchit Puengnathong,</i>

01:07:05.160 --> 01:07:07.280
<i>a member of staff at Sahamongkol Music.</i>

01:07:07.360 --> 01:07:08.600
Why are you doing this?

01:07:08.680 --> 01:07:12.360
<i>Congratulations.</i>
<i>You’ve made it to level nine.</i>

01:07:12.400 --> 01:07:14.320
<i>This next level is a cinch.</i>

01:07:14.400 --> 01:07:18.160
<i>You must find our assistant,</i>
<i>who is somewhere in this hospital and--</i>

01:07:18.240 --> 01:07:20.320
Look, this has gotten out of hand.

01:07:20.400 --> 01:07:24.240
<i>If you are caught, then the game is over.</i>

01:07:24.280 --> 01:07:26.360
<i>If you are able to find our assistant,</i>

01:07:26.440 --> 01:07:29.520
<i>not only will you have</i>
<i>an important tool for playing level ten,</i>

01:07:30.200 --> 01:07:33.160
<i>but you will also receive 10 million Baht.</i>

01:07:33.240 --> 01:07:35.120
<i>From here on, every three minutes,</i>

01:07:35.160 --> 01:07:36.600
<i>we will send you a clue.</i>

01:07:36.680 --> 01:07:37.760
Hey, wait a minute. Wait.

01:07:38.000 --> 01:07:39.760
<i>How’s that?</i>
<i>If you’re ready then let’s get started,</i>

01:07:39.960 --> 01:07:42.280
<i>to listen again, please press 1.</i>

01:07:43.320 --> 01:07:45.680
<i>Spread out</i>
<i>and block the exits of the hospital.</i>

01:07:45.760 --> 01:07:49.280
<i>Be careful, the suspect</i>
<i>may try to take patients hostage.</i>

01:07:54.480 --> 01:07:57.760
<i>The first clue word is "eight". Press 1…</i>

01:08:44.680 --> 01:08:47.360
Hey! Quickly! Catch him!

01:08:55.200 --> 01:08:56.280
Hey! Follow him!

01:09:02.560 --> 01:09:04.400
Quick! Get him!

01:09:05.040 --> 01:09:06.560
Hey! Stop!

01:09:20.560 --> 01:09:23.080
Spread out
and search every inch of this place.

01:09:23.160 --> 01:09:26.520
Let's go. You, come with me.

01:09:34.480 --> 01:09:37.360
Nothing out of the ordinary here.

01:10:31.040 --> 01:10:33.640
It-- It's a zombie!

01:10:33.720 --> 01:10:37.160
<i>The next clue word is "zero".</i>

01:10:37.240 --> 01:10:38.360
What the hell is going on?

01:10:38.440 --> 01:10:42.280
We can never have
too many officers on this guy.

01:10:43.600 --> 01:10:47.600
<i>We won’t have enough police</i>
<i>for other cases, Surachai.</i>

01:10:47.680 --> 01:10:49.080
<i>Aren't you overreacting a bit?</i>

01:10:49.120 --> 01:10:52.760
Sir, I’m positive
that the capture of Mr. Phuchit

01:10:52.840 --> 01:10:56.120
will lead us to solving
a far more significant case.

01:10:56.680 --> 01:10:58.720
Do you have evidence to back this up?

01:10:59.640 --> 01:11:01.680
Of course, sir.

01:11:03.680 --> 01:11:06.400
Fine. I'll give you some leeway.

01:11:22.080 --> 01:11:24.000
-Hello?
-<i>Your last clue word</i>

01:11:24.080 --> 01:11:27.520
-<i>is "five". To listen again, press 1.</i>
-Five?

01:11:28.200 --> 01:11:31.440
Five. That’s it?

01:11:48.800 --> 01:11:52.840
805. 805.

01:12:56.360 --> 01:12:57.680
What happened?

01:12:57.720 --> 01:12:59.720
Hey!

01:12:59.800 --> 01:13:02.960
Don't be afraid. Just tell me everything.

01:13:24.400 --> 01:13:26.040
Tell everyone to be ready.

01:13:26.120 --> 01:13:27.760
The suspect has got to be nearby.

01:13:28.000 --> 01:13:29.280
Sir.

01:13:35.480 --> 01:13:36.720
Telephone, sir.

01:13:39.480 --> 01:13:40.720
Yes, sir.

01:14:42.560 --> 01:14:45.000
Hey, there. Where are you off to?

01:14:45.480 --> 01:14:47.640
My nephew has come to pick me up.

01:14:49.360 --> 01:14:50.560
Be careful,

01:14:50.640 --> 01:14:53.280
there is a criminal on the loose.

01:14:53.360 --> 01:14:57.320
Take good care of her, buddy?

01:15:25.480 --> 01:15:27.080
Call off the search.

01:15:28.200 --> 01:15:29.640
Yes, sir.

01:16:12.480 --> 01:16:14.280
Tum, let me borrow your car.

01:16:14.360 --> 01:16:16.280
Where are you going?

01:16:16.320 --> 01:16:18.160
To look for a friend. I’ll be right back.

01:16:19.760 --> 01:16:21.640
Okay, but be quick.

01:16:21.720 --> 01:16:25.280
And watch out,
because your stupid dog got out.

01:16:25.320 --> 01:16:28.360
Why didn't you go after him?

01:16:28.400 --> 01:16:32.680
No. Mom says he's an animal.

01:16:32.760 --> 01:16:35.720
He’s just looking for a mate.
He’ll be back when he’s done.

01:16:39.000 --> 01:16:43.000
What are you looking at?
The car keys are over there.

01:16:45.000 --> 01:16:46.120
<i>It's not difficult.</i>

01:16:46.200 --> 01:16:49.480
<i>Just do what the old woman wants.</i>
<i>That’s it.</i>

01:16:49.560 --> 01:16:51.160
No one else is going to get hurt, right?

01:16:51.240 --> 01:16:55.080
<i>Not at all. The old woman</i>
<i>is not the violent type.</i>

01:16:55.120 --> 01:16:57.120
Then it's dark, then it's blurry,
then it's bright.

01:16:58.120 --> 01:17:00.120
Then it's bright.

01:17:00.160 --> 01:17:01.120
Grandma.

01:17:01.160 --> 01:17:02.400
Wow, the stars in the sky…

01:17:02.480 --> 01:17:05.160
So where is this hut
you keep talking about?

01:17:05.200 --> 01:17:06.760
…are so pretty.

01:17:06.960 --> 01:17:08.080
Granny.

01:17:27.440 --> 01:17:31.360
Why did you leave
the clothes out like this?

